&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; an &#39;unsupported
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; scheme&#39; message.
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; We could do with some clean up in here.  Currently all URI
&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; exceptions
